com.team23.weather.models

Class MarsForecast

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team23.weather.models.MarsForecast

  • public class MarsForecast
extends Object
    A MarsForecast represents all the weather information on Mars as described in the project specifications. This includes the date of the forecast (Earth and Mars), the minimum and maximum Temperature's, the Pressure, the humidity, the wind Speed, the wind direction, and the sky condition. This forecast is then displayed to the user on the MarsForecastPanel.
    Author:
    Andrew Bloch-Hansen
    See Also:
    MarsWeatherClient, MarsWeatherResponse, Report, MarsForecastPanel
